channel.title: Eco-reset wont work
channel.description:
Okay so my economy reset is in a file called Economy Reset, I had the EconomyReset.java file, and I compiled it to be a .class when I run the EcoReset.bat it says [code]Error: Could not find or load main class EconomyReset Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
My EcoReset.bat file has this coding
[code]@echo off title Eco Reset java EconomyReset pause[/code]
Any idea on how to get it working?
